    <!-- Assumptions Note -->
    <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow p-5 text-center">
      <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">
        <strong>Calculation assumptions:</strong> Average tariff ₹7.5/unit | On-Grid ₹58,000/kWp | Off-Grid ₹95,000/kWp | Hybrid ₹78,000/kWp |
        Generation 1,500 kWh/kW/year | Residential subsidy up to ₹78,000 (PM Surya Ghar) only for On-Grid.
        Actual costs may vary based on site survey, roof condition, and component selection.
      </p>
    </div>

